{"tid":1825001,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【國際戰線建議】Stand with Hong Kong, Boycott China!","createTime":"2020-01-15T02:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T08:00:54.000Z","uid":212944,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"92fb9d01c1c696e57e360661562f05368d6c0667","tid":1825001,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"琴日見到一路出唔少高質文嘅巴打 愛情波函數 出左呢個post，話打悲情牌已經無用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">悲情國際文宣已經開始過時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824457/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824457/page/1</a></span><br />\n其實小弟都深表認同<br />\n畢竟望一望國際形勢，情況比我地差嘅國家真係好多，好似智利、伊朗、伊拉克、巴勒斯坦咁。下下開實彈，人地無gear無盛，D tear gas 成粒射入個腦到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係因為我地感覺上應該係一個先進發達地區，但都發生D第三世界先有嘅野，所以一開始會有好大震撼。<br />\n<br />\n其實而家國際社會都已經基本上認同我地好慘，同埋大部分會支持我地<br />\n所以我地下一步應該要將<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢股憤怒轉發為佢地實際嘅行動</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 手足已經發起咗一個叫做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> #ABC_Challenge</span></strong></span>，即係Anywhere but China，呼籲大家抵制中國製產品。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有班on9仔女喺twitter開始咗個challenge <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1815702/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1815702/page/1</a></span><br />\n<br />\n但我自己就覺得依然係太空泛，而且個challenge係<span style=\"color: gold;\">「影低你身邊任何唔係中國製既產品，然後po上twitter，順便tag 3個Twitter 手足」</span>，感覺上好似有D流，因為佢只要身上有一件唔係made in China嘅product就得，都做唔到boycott China嘅效果。<br />\n要真正將呢個方向發揚光大，我建議做以下嘅嘢：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 之後嘅遊行，我地嘅口號唔再叫 &quot;Fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong' ，而係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&quot;Stand with Hong Kong. Boycott China&quot;</span> </span></strong><br />\n呢到用左類似頂真既手法，其實係心理學上係暗示緊我地要遞進落去下一個階段，亦都係可以召集所有同中共企於對立面既盟友，例如台灣<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 用杯葛TVB既方法，尋找唔同中資企業，一波波咁杯葛</span></span></strong><br />\n好處：行動清晰具體，而且容易出文宣<br />\n<br />\n示例：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> #DeleteTikTok </span></span></strong><br />\n我認為第一間我地可以鼓勵外國人杯葛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抖音 Tik Tok</span></strong></span><br />\n香港人成日笑抖音係抖陰，但事實係好多鬼佬都用Tik Tok<br />\n就連Pewdiepie都係出咗個series係post Tik Tok既片<br />\n<br />\n但早前Tik Tok 國際版 censor咗一段講維吾爾集中營嘅片，又有人發現你一download左個app，佢就會拎晒你既個人資料<br />\n<br />\n所以我地第一波行動應該係鼓勵所有人Delete Tik Tok<br />\n呢個行動不但簡單<br />\n而且容易睇出個成效<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<br />\n不如一齊討論下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee689f33ee7366803639fc005e7a590b81ad368","tid":1825001,"uid":212944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:15:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>Stand with Hong Kong<br />\nBoycott China<br />\n<br />\nDelete Tik Tok</strong>"},{"pid":"28b6bc6628e4a64a32b1ecf50a99a3140c29a77b","tid":1825001,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>Stand with Hong Kong, Boycott China!<br />\nDelete Tit Tok!</strong>"},{"pid":"aacb620269a40c9f7d0faf97d0dfd54bab726c15","tid":1825001,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>Stand with Hong Kong, Boycott China!<br />\nDelete Tit Tok!</strong>"},{"pid":"4593ae6816ba11ba50fda45f2d5f90c1f3ead5c4","tid":1825001,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:17:35.000Z","msg":"杯葛中國應該係我地而家既新方向"},{"pid":"3c670c3810e1ec5d655efeb1285c3c4ceb9627e7","tid":1825001,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:19:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【<span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span>】好多<span style=\"color: red;\">白人左翼</span>抹黑<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1</a></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b71a70afb87cebcd6cf8c8c2fdbc4874bfd9762a","tid":1825001,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:23:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.19 遮打道<br />\n1.22 荔枝角收押所</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwugtoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwugtoH.jpg&h=a3dfe053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Eq7z3V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Eq7z3V.jpg&h=6484967a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XmELBM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXmELBM2.jpg&h=0edbf756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">*連儂廁<br />\n*Twitter戰線<br />\n好 重 要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃店賀年食品</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rY7TRFB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrY7TRFB.png&h=7e3a6ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4smjXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4smjXK.jpg&h=8185216a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yVFbHa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyVFbHa5.png&h=19cbaa2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6b09b25bbc84d2347198b676f86e3f8508da20d","tid":1825001,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:23:20.000Z","msg":"1/5"},{"pid":"7f014c0b94053a0a731509022997ba1b0cd2595d","tid":1825001,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"2/5"},{"pid":"a6db820e1459c353bf4e03114